TION> Commission </ORGANIZATION>, which represents <LOCATION> U.S. </LOCATION> oil producers. The commission's semi-annual gathering will be held through Wednesday Its chairman is <LOCATION> Alaska </LOCATION> Gov. <PERSON> Steve </PERSON> <PERSON> Cowper </PERSON>, who gave an overview Monday of the Exxon Valdez oil spill in <LOCATION> Prince </LOCATION> <LOCATION> William </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Sound </LOCATION> and its cleanu-up efforts. <PERSON> Cowper </PERSON> said the spill pointed out the need for more environmental safeguards but warned they would drive up oil production costs.
